data.description: Welcome to this wonderfully updated 3 bedroom home. Located in one of the most coveted areas of Chugiak, sitting on a quiet cul-de-sac. This property also features an oversized garage, providing ample space for all your storage needs. The master bedroom and bathroom are conveniently located on the main floor. The home features multiple living spaces perfect for entertaining. Outside you will....find a beautifully landscaped yard, with an RV pad for extra parking. As well as a hot tub on the back deck for relaxing after a long day!
